USE DATABASECOUNTRYHL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CURRENCY') AND O.NAME = 'FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYCU_COUNTRY')
ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYCU_COUNTRY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CURRENCY') AND O.NAME = 'FK_COUNTRY__CURRENCYC_CURRENCY')
ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__CURRENCYC_CURRENCY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CURRENCY')
AND NAME = 'CURRENCYCOUNTRY_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY_CURRENCY.CURRENCYCOUNTRY_FK
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CURRENCY')
AND NAME = 'COUNTRYCURRENCY_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY_CURRENCY.COUNTRYCURRENCY_FK
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
DROP CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_CURRENCY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSOBJECTS
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_CURRENCY')
AND TYPE = 'U')
DROP TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: COUNTRY_CURRENCY */
/*==============================================================*/
CREATE TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY (
CCU_ID INT IDENTITY,
COU_ID INT NOT NULL,
CUR_ID INT NOT NULL
)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
ADD CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_CURRENCY PRIMARY KEY (CCU_ID)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: COUNTRYCURRENCY_FK */
/*==============================================================*/




CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX COUNTRYCURRENCY_FK ON COUNTRY_CURRENCY (COU_ID ASC)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: CURRENCYCOUNTRY_FK */
/*==============================================================*/




CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX CURRENCYCOUNTRY_FK ON COUNTRY_CURRENCY (CUR_ID ASC)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYCU_COUNTRY FOREIGN KEY (COU_ID)
REFERENCES COUNTRY (COU_ID)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_CURRENCY
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__CURRENCYC_CURRENCY FOREIGN KEY (CUR_ID)
REFERENCES CURRENCY (CUR_ID)
go
